co.paralleluniverse.concurrent.util

Class AbstractCompletableExecutorService

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.util.concurrent.AbstractExecutorService
      • co.paralleluniverse.concurrent.util.AbstractCompletableExecutorService
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    CompletableExecutorService, Executor, ExecutorService

    public abstract class AbstractCompletableExecutorService
extends AbstractExecutorService
implements CompletableExecutorService

    Implements CompletableExecutorService execution methods atop the abstract Executor.execute(java.lang.Runnable) method. More concretely, the submit, invokeAny and invokeAll methods create CompletableFutureTask instances and pass them to Executor.execute(java.lang.Runnable).

    In addition to Executor.execute(java.lang.Runnable), subclasses must implement all methods related to shutdown and termination.
